<eesti>&sect; 1. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 1. </inglise>
<eesti>Erim&auml;rgistamise objekt </eesti>
<inglise>Object to be marked with fiscal marker </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Erim&auml;rgistamisele kuulub Eestisse imporditav ja Eestis toodetav kerge k&uuml;tte&otilde;li ning see osa diislik&uuml;tusest, mis on ette n&auml;htud kasutamiseks traktorites ja p&otilde;llut&ouml;&ouml;masinates ning kutselisel kalap&uuml;&uuml;gil vastavalt k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 3 s&auml;testatule (edaspidi eriotstarbeline diislik&uuml;tus). </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Light heating oil imported into Estonia or manufactured in Estonia and the part of diesel fuel which is intended for use in tractors and agricultural machinery and upon commercial fishing pursuant to the provisions of subsection (3) of this section (hereinafter diesel fuel for specific purposes) is subject to fiscal marking. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud kerget k&uuml;tte&otilde;li on keelatud kasutada mootorik&uuml;tusena s&otilde;iduautos ning reisijate- v&otilde;i kaubaveoks etten&auml;htud s&otilde;idukis (edaspidi s&otilde;iduk) liiklusseaduse (RT 1992, 12, 193; RT I 1995, 2/3, 3; 1996, 16, 268; 1997, 86, 1459; 1999, 16, 272) m&otilde;istes, v&auml;lja arvatud traktoris. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) It is prohibited to use light heating oil specified in subsection (1) of this section as motor fuel in automobiles and vehicles used for the carriage of passengers or goods (hereinafter vehicles) as defined in the Traffic Act (RT 1992, 12, 193; RT I 1995, 2/3, 3; 1996, 16, 268; 1997, 86, 1459; 1999, 16, 272), except in tractors. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud eriotstarbelist diislik&uuml;tust on lubatud kasutada ainult traktorites ja p&otilde;llut&ouml;&ouml;masinates ning &auml;riseadustikus (RT I 1995, 26-28, 355; RT I 1998, 91-93, 1500; 1999, 10, 155; 23, 355; 24, 360; 57, 596; 102, 907; 2000, 29, 172; 49, 303; 55, 365; 57, 373; 2001, 34, 185; 56, 332 ja 336) s&auml;testatud korras registreeritud ettev&otilde;tjal kutselisel kalap&uuml;&uuml;gil kalap&uuml;&uuml;giseaduse (RT I 1995, 80, 1384; 1996, 27, 567; 1998, 108/109, 1784; 1999, 10, 152; 54, 583; 95, 843; 2000, 13, 92; 54, 348; 81, 514; 2001, 18, 88) t&auml;henduses. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Diesel fuel for specific purposes specified in subsection (1) of this section may be used only in tractors and agricultural machinery and by undertakings registered pursuant to the procedure provided for in the Commercial Code (RT I 1995, 26-28, 355; RT I 1998, 91-93, 1500; 1999, 10, 155; 23, 355; 24, 360; 57, 596; 102, 907; 2000, 29, 172; 49, 303; 55, 365; 57, 373; 2001, 34, 185; 56, 332 and 336) upon commercial fishing within the meaning of the Fishing Act (RT I 1995, 80, 1384; 1996, 27, 567; 1998, 108/109, 1784; 1999, 10, 152; 54, 583; 95, 843; 2000, 13, 92; 54, 348; 81, 514; 2001, 18, 88). </inglise>
<eesti>K&otilde;igil muudel juhtudel on eriotstarbelise diislik&uuml;tuse kasutamine keelatud. </eesti>
<inglise>In all other cases, use of diesel fuel for specific purposes is prohibited. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.04.2000 j&otilde;ust.25.04.2000 - RT I 2000, 33, 199) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.04.2000 entered into force 25.04.2000 - RT I 2000, 33, 199) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 2. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 2. </inglise>
<eesti>Erim&auml;rgistamine </eesti>
<inglise>Fiscal marking </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Erim&auml;rgistamine on kerge k&uuml;tte&otilde;li ja eriotstarbelise diislik&uuml;tuse eristamine teistest vedelk&uuml;tustest nendesse lisaainete lisamise teel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Fiscal marking is the differentiation of light heating oil and diesel fuel for specific purposes from other types of liquid fuel by putting additives therein. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kergele k&uuml;tte&otilde;lile ja eriotstarbelisele diislik&uuml;tusele erim&auml;rgistamiseks lisatavate ainete loetelu ning kontsentratsiooni kerges k&uuml;tte&otilde;lis ja diislik&uuml;tuses kehtestab Vabariigi Valitsus m&auml;&auml;rusega. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The list and concentration of additives added to light heating oil and diesel fuel for specific purposes for fiscal marking shall be established by a regulation of the Government of the Republic. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.04.2000 j&otilde;ust.25.04.2000 - RT I 2000, 33, 199) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.04.2000 entered into force 25.04.2000 - RT I 2000, 33, 199) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 3. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 3. </inglise>
<eesti>Erim&auml;rgistamise korraldus </eesti>
<inglise>Organisation of fiscal marking </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Eestisse on lubatud importida vabasse ringlusse lubamise tolliprotseduuriga tolliseadustiku m&otilde;istes sellist kerget k&uuml;tte&otilde;li ja eriotstarbelist diislik&uuml;tust, mis on k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 2 l&otilde;ikes 2 nimetatud lisaainetega erim&auml;rgistatud enne selle kerge k&uuml;tte&otilde;li ja eriotstarbelise diislik&uuml;tuse toimetamist Eesti tolliterritooriumile (edaspidi tolliterritoorium) v&otilde;i erim&auml;rgistatakse tolliterritooriumil. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Light heating oil and diesel fuel for specific purposes which are marked with the additives specified in subsection 2 (2) of this Act before entry into the Estonian customs territory (hereinafter customs territory) or are marked with a fiscal marker in the customs territory may be imported into Estonia under the customs procedure of release for free circulation as defined in the Customs Code. </inglise>
<eesti>(17.10.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.07.2002 - RT I 2001, 88, 531) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.10.2001 entered into force 01.07.2002 - RT I 2001, 88, 531) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Enne kerge k&uuml;tte&otilde;li ja eriotstarbelise diislik&uuml;tuse toimetamist tolliterritooriumile v&otilde;ib vabaks ringluseks etten&auml;htud kerget k&uuml;tte&otilde;li ja eriotstarbelist diislik&uuml;tust erim&auml;rgistada v&auml;lisriigis. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Before the entry of light heating oil and diesel fuel for specific purposes into the customs territory, the light heating oil and diesel fuel for specific purposes intended for free circulation may be marked with a fiscal marker in a foreign state. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;lisriigis erim&auml;rgistatud kerge k&uuml;tte&otilde;li ja eriotstarbelise diislik&uuml;tuse erim&auml;rgistamise eest vastutab vastavalt kerge k&uuml;tte&otilde;li v&otilde;i eriotstarbelise diislik&uuml;tuse importija. </eesti>
<inglise>The importer of the light heating oil or diesel fuel for specific purposes, respectively, is responsible for the marking of the light heating oil or diesel fuel for specific purposes with a fiscal marker in a foreign state. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Tolliterritooriumile toimetatud vabasse ringlusse lubamiseks etten&auml;htud erim&auml;rgistamata kerge k&uuml;tte&otilde;li ja eriotstarbeline diislik&uuml;tus erim&auml;rgistatakse tolliterminalis v&otilde;i tollilaos. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Light heating oil and diesel fuel for specific purposes which have been brought into the customs territory, are intended for release for free circulation and which are not marked with a fiscal marker shall be marked with a fiscal marker in a customs terminal or customs warehouse. </inglise>
<eesti>Kerge k&uuml;tte&otilde;li ja eriotstarbelise diislik&uuml;tuse erim&auml;rgistamise eest tolliterminalis v&otilde;i tollilaos vastutab vastavalt tolliterminali v&otilde;i tollilao pidaja. </eesti>
<inglise>The keeper of the customs terminal or customs warehouse, respectively, is responsible for the marking of light heating oil and diesel fuel for specific purposes with a fiscal marker in the customs terminal or customs warehouse. </inglise>
<eesti>(17.10.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.07.2002 - RT I 2001, 88, 531) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.10.2001 entered into force 01.07.2002 - RT I 2001, 88, 531) </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Eestis toodetav kerge k&uuml;tte&otilde;li ja eriotstarbeline diislik&uuml;tus erim&auml;rgistatakse tootmise kohas hiljemalt k&uuml;tuse v&auml;ljastamisel. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Light heating oil and diesel fuel for specific purposes manufactured in Estonia shall be marked with a fiscal marker in the place of manufacture not later than upon the delivery of such fuel. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Eestis toodetava kerge k&uuml;tte&otilde;li ja eriotstarbelise diislik&uuml;tuse erim&auml;rgistamise eest vastutab tootja. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The manufacturer is responsible for the fiscal marking of light heating oil and diesel fuel for specific purposes manufactured in Estonia. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kerge k&uuml;tte&otilde;li ja eriotstarbelise diislik&uuml;tuse erim&auml;rgistamise ning selle &uuml;le kontrolli teostamise korra kehtestab Vabariigi Valitsus v&otilde;i tema volitusel rahandusminister m&auml;&auml;rusega. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) The procedure for the fiscal marking of light heating oil and diesel fuel for specific purposes and for the exercise of supervision thereof shall be established by a regulation of the Government of Republic or, on the authorisation thereof, the Minister of Finance. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.04.2000 j&otilde;ust.25.04.2000 - RT I 2000, 33, 199) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.04.2000 entered into force 25.04.2000 - RT I 2000, 33, 199) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 4. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 4. </inglise>
<eesti>Erim&auml;rgistamise kontrollimine </eesti>
<inglise>Supervision over fiscal marking </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Tolliamet kontrollib tolliformaalsuste k&auml;igus kerge k&uuml;tte&otilde;li ja eriotstarbelise diislik&uuml;tuse erim&auml;rgistatust ning teostab j&auml;relevalvet tolliterminalis v&otilde;i tollilaos toimuva erim&auml;rgistamise &uuml;le. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) In the course of customs formalities, the Customs Board shall monitor the marking of light heating oil and diesel fuel for specific purposes with a fiscal marker and exercise supervision over fiscal marking carried out in customs terminals and customs warehouses. </inglise>
<eesti>(17.10.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.07.2002 - RT I 2001, 88, 531) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.10.2001 entered into force 01.07.2002 - RT I 2001, 88, 531) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) J&auml;relevalvet Eestis toodetava kerge k&uuml;tte&otilde;li ja eriotstarbelise diislik&uuml;tuse erim&auml;rgistamise &uuml;le teostab Maksuamet. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Tax Board shall exercise supervision over the fiscal marking of light heating oil and diesel fuel for specific purposes manufactured in Estonia. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.04.2000 j&otilde;ust.25.04.2000 - RT I 2000, 33, 199) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.04.2000 entered into force 25.04.2000 - RT I 2000, 33, 199) </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Politseiametnikul, abipolitseinikul, tolliametnikul ja maksuametnikul on &otilde;igus v&otilde;tta s&otilde;iduki k&uuml;tuses&uuml;steemist, sealhulgas k&uuml;tusepaagist (edaspidi k&uuml;tuses&uuml;steem), proove selles s&otilde;idukis mootorik&uuml;tusena kasutatava k&uuml;tuse erim&auml;rgistatuse kindlakstegemiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Police officials, special constables, customs officials and taxation officials have the right to take samples from the fuel system of a vehicle, including from the fuel tank (hereinafter fuel system), to ascertain whether the fuel used as motor fuel in the vehicle is marked with a fiscal marker. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Politseiamet ja Tolliamet edastavad Maksuametile iga kuu 15. kuup&auml;evaks nende juriidiliste isikute ja f&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust ettev&otilde;tjate nimed, kellele kuuluva s&otilde;iduki k&uuml;tuses&uuml;steemis eelmisel kuul avastati erim&auml;rgistatud k&uuml;tus. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The Police Administration and Customs Board shall, by the fifteenth day of each month, send to the Tax Board the names of the legal persons and sole proprietors in the fuel systems of whose vehicles fuel marked with a fiscal marker is discovered. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) S&otilde;idukis mootorik&uuml;tusena kasutatava k&uuml;tuse erim&auml;rgistatuse kindlakstegemise korra kehtestab Vabariigi Valitsus. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The Government of the Republic establishes the procedure for ascertaining whether the fuel used as motor fuel in a vehicle is marked with a fiscal marker. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 5. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 5. </inglise>
<eesti>Proovi v&otilde;tmise erikord ja k&uuml;tuse vahetamine </eesti>
<inglise>Special sampling procedure and change of fuel </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kui proovi v&otilde;tmine s&otilde;iduki k&uuml;tuses&uuml;steemist osutub kohapeal v&otilde;imatuks, on k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahv 4 l&otilde;ikes 3 nimetatud isikutel &otilde;igus anda s&otilde;idukijuhile korraldus toimetada s&otilde;iduk l&auml;himasse kohta, kus selle k&uuml;tuses&uuml;steemist on v&otilde;imalik proove v&otilde;tta. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) If it is impossible to take samples from the fuel system of a vehicle on site, the persons specified in subsection 4 (3) of this Act have the right to order the driver of the vehicle to take the vehicle to the nearest site where it is possible to take samples from the fuel system. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kui s&otilde;iduki k&uuml;tuses&uuml;steemis avastatakse erim&auml;rgistatud k&uuml;tus, on selle s&otilde;iduki juht kohustatud vahetama k&uuml;tuses&uuml;steemis oleva k&uuml;tuse 24 tunni jooksul avastamise hetkest arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) If fuel marked with a fiscal marker is discovered in the fuel system of a vehicle, the driver of the vehicle is required to change the fuel in the fuel system within twenty-four hours from the moment of discovery. </inglise>
<eesti>Erim&auml;rgistatud k&uuml;tuse avastanud isik on kohustatud andma s&otilde;idukijuhile dokumendi, millele on m&auml;rgitud k&uuml;tuses&uuml;steemis oleva erim&auml;rgistatud k&uuml;tuse avastamise kuup&auml;ev ja kellaaeg. </eesti>
<inglise>The person who discovers fuel marked with a fiscal marker is required to give the driver a document which indicates the date and time the marked fuel is discovered in the fuel system. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 6. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 6. </inglise>
<eesti>Seaduse rakendamise erisused v&auml;lisriigis registreeritud s&otilde;iduki puhul </eesti>
<inglise>Specifications for application of Act for vehicles registered in foreign states </inglise>
<eesti>(1) V&auml;lisriigis registreeritud s&otilde;iduki, mille k&uuml;tuses&uuml;steemis on avastatud erim&auml;rgistatud k&uuml;tus, v&otilde;ib tolliterritooriumilt v&auml;lja lubada p&auml;rast nimetatud rikkumisega seotud asjaolude selgitamist ja selle rikkumise eest m&auml;&auml;ratud rahatrahvi maksmist. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A vehicle registered in a foreign state in the fuel system of which fuel marked with a fiscal marker is discovered may be permitted to leave the customs territory after the clarification of circumstances concerning such violation and payment of a fine imposed for the violation. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kui v&auml;lisriigis registreeritud s&otilde;iduki juht on lahkunud tolliterritooriumilt enne k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud rikkumise eest temale m&auml;&auml;ratud rahatrahvi maksmist, lubatakse tal p&ouml;&ouml;rduda tolliterritooriumile vaid tingimusel, et see rahatrahv on makstud. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) If the driver of a vehicle registered in a foreign state leaves the customs territory before payment of the fine imposed on him or her for the violation specified in subsection (1) of this section, he or she shall be permitted to enter the customs territory only on the condition that the fine is paid. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 6 (1). </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 6 (1). </inglise>
<eesti>Eriotstarbelise diislik&uuml;tuse m&uuml;&uuml;mine </eesti>
<inglise>Sale of diesel fuel for specific purposes </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Eriotstarbelise diislik&uuml;tuse m&uuml;&uuml;gi korra kehtestab Vabariigi Valitsus v&otilde;i tema poolt volitatud minister. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The procedure for the sale of diesel fuel for specific purposes shall be established by the Government of the Republic or a minister authorised by the Government of the Republic. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Eriotstarbelise diislik&uuml;tuse k&auml;ibemaksuta m&uuml;&uuml;gihind on sama m&uuml;&uuml;ja poolt m&uuml;&uuml;dava erim&auml;rgistamata diislik&uuml;tuse k&auml;ibemaksuta m&uuml;&uuml;gihinnast madalam v&auml;hemalt m&auml;rgistamata ja eriotstarbelise diislik&uuml;tuse kehtiva aktsiisim&auml;&auml;ra erinevuse v&otilde;rra. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The sales price, exclusive of value added tax, of diesel fuel for specific purposes shall be lower than the sales price, exclusive of value added tax, of diesel fuel without a fiscal marker sold by the same seller at least by the difference between the valid excise duty rate of diesel fuel without a fiscal marker and diesel fuel for specific purposes. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.04.2000 j&otilde;ust.25.04.2000 - RT I 2000, 33, 199) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.04.2000 entered into force 25.04.2000 - RT I 2000, 33, 199) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 7. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 7. </inglise>
<eesti>Vastutus </eesti>
<inglise>Liability </inglise>
<eesti>(1) F&uuml;&uuml;siline isik vastutab k&auml;esoleva seaduse rikkumise eest haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste seadustiku paragrahv 92 (8) alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Natural persons are held liable for violation of this Act pursuant to &sect; 92 (8) of the Code of Administrative Offences. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Juriidiline isik vastutab k&auml;esoleva seaduse rikkumise eest maksukorralduse seaduse paragrahv 30 l&otilde;ike 1 punkti 12 alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Legal persons are held liable for violation of this Act pursuant to clause 30 (1) 12) of the Taxation Act. </inglise>
<eesti>F&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust ettev&otilde;tja vastutab k&auml;esoleva seaduse rikkumise eest maksukorralduse seaduse alusel selles juriidilisele isikule etten&auml;htud sanktsiooni piires. </eesti>
<inglise>Sole proprietors are held liable for violation of this Act pursuant to the procedure provided for in the Taxation Act within the limits of the sanctions prescribed for legal persons. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kui f&uuml;&uuml;siline isik, tegutsedes juriidilise isiku v&otilde;i f&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust ettev&otilde;tja nimel v&otilde;i huvides, rikkus k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;udeid, v&otilde;ib selle rikkumise asjas kohaldada karistust samaaegselt nii f&uuml;&uuml;silisele kui ka juriidilisele isikule v&otilde;i f&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust ettev&otilde;tjale selleks etten&auml;htud sanktsiooni piires. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) If a natural person violates the requirements of this Act when acting in the name or interest of a legal person or sole proprietor, punishment for such violation may be imposed on both the natural person, and the legal person or sole proprietor within the limits of the prescribed sanction. </inglise>
<eesti>[ &sect; 8 v&auml;lja j&auml;etud ] (1) </eesti>
<inglise>[ &sect; 8 omitted ] (2) </inglise>
